{"tid":1383182,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"滅火隊請進","createTime":"2019-07-29T15:47:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T16:35:10.000Z","uid":28648,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"dce79af03ef3513eeb0735764c934fae1afc640c","tid":1383182,"uid":28648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:47:31.000Z","msg":"為左俾其他行山人士知道你係專業既滅火隊，<br />\n有效加快滅火控煙既速度，<br />\n唔該你配戴<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">紅色閃燈</span></span>，以供識別<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Duz0xRk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDuz0xRk.png&h=05413943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n野餐時記得注意山火喔<br />\n<br />\n其他行山o士記得唔好自己搞個火頭，<br />\n俾專業既處理！"},{"pid":"6136088553e904985bef2d1f358ca3bd0988265a","tid":1383182,"uid":28648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:55:48.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"cb652f748db0b820d15adaaf6469bb8971db4d45","tid":1383182,"uid":178684,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T15:57:00.000Z","msg":"先生/小姐，我而家跟據警察通例 Police General Orders 第20章 第14條要求你出示委任證，麻煩請你合作。<br />\n如果你無法出示委任證，根據香港法例第228章 第22條，我有合理理由懷疑你干犯假冒公職人員罪。<br />\n<br />\nRepeat 到佢出示委任證。"},{"pid":"3c069b7c60b6e00fa2c15b677f5c3218b30182c4","tid":1383182,"uid":28648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:05:39.000Z","msg":"我無野講<br />\n我好唔舒服，要去醫院"},{"pid":"05aaf6ac2243e9414a8008d9ac3b5b20225848bf","tid":1383182,"uid":28648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:32:06.000Z","msg":"認真 po 無人覆"},{"pid":"2551f57158c036337d766de2349645609e5936c1","tid":1383182,"uid":28648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:34:18.000Z","msg":"光"},{"pid":"abb74a5b91c338993d45837fec57782f910a6cb8","tid":1383182,"uid":28648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:34:28.000Z","msg":"復"},{"pid":"c92f0cfb701814fb81065470f67dd1e4a3238b7b","tid":1383182,"uid":28648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:34:38.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"52e95d34d98d3338069b17b1b79d8969bfcaa75f","tid":1383182,"uid":28648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T16:35:10.000Z","msg":"港"}]}